name: The Veggies: Wrong Medium
description: I guess the Edible Class of Characters(edible being a relative term, obviously) from "The Veggies" have no idea what the fuck is happening, per usual. So many clashing mediums from 3D pen, Oculus Quest 2, procreate, and two twisted minds.. Brain__Pudding and Susanne Cummings. Please, let this image take you on a weird journey of your own. Starring Kevin(the corn), PJ(the pea), Beani(the bean), Carl(the carrot), Pickle Ricky(the pickle), and Zombie Tots(the zombie potato that committed suicide and just can't stay dead)!
